snippet.title: Adding Juice - An Elaborate History of Chess - DevLog 4
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1255020/An_Elaborate_History_of_Chess/

In this dev log we cover some of the things we've added recently to make An Elaborate History of Chess a little more juicy and fun to interact with!

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/f2hdFN6
Check out our last game Paper Pirates: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1234220/Paper_Pirates/

Drop some ideas below! :)
#gamedev #indiedev #devlog 

Music: Ballad of the Goddess by Mikel https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eAchq6sH_iU&ab_channel=GameChops
